lass=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 04, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104agv1665703005070.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/agv1665703005070.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/agv1665703005070.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"agv1665703005070\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"agv1665703005070__goto_223617\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Branch unconditionally to the specified label.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"agv1665703005070__topic_d73388e1_d73389e1_d73390e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"agv1665703005070__p_d73391e1_d73392e1_d73393e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">goto</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Label</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"agv1665703005070__section_w2333ab1b7b5_w2334ab1b7_w2335ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"agv1665703005070__p_d73394e1_d73395e1_d73396e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">goto start</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agv1665703005070__topic_d48247e1_d48248e1_d48249e1_d48250e1_d48251e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d121874e79\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"agv1665703005070__table_d6710e1_d6711e1_d6712e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"agv1665703005070__table_d6710e1_d6711e1_d6712e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"agv1665703005070__table_d6710e1_d6711e1_d6712e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"agv1665703005070__table_d6710e1_d6711e1_d6712e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agv1665703005070__table_d6710e1_d6711e1_d6712e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Label</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agv1665703005070__table_d6710e1_d6711e1_d6712e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agv1665703005070__table_d6710e1_d6711e1_d6712e1__entry__3\"> Label of a statement in the current ProcScript\n                        module. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agv1665703005070__topic_d48252e1_d48253e1_d48254e1_d48255e1_d48256e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d121874e133\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"agv1665703005070__d5966e20\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agv1665703005070__topic_d48257e1_d48258e1_d48259e1_d48260e1_d48261e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d121874e143\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"agv1665703005070__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agv1665703005070__topic_d48262e1_d48263e1_d48264e1_d48265e1_d48266e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d121874e152\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"agv1665703005070__p_d73415e1_d73416e1_d73417e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">goto</span> statement continues execution within the current ProcScript module, beginning at the statement identified by <var class=\"keyword varname\">Label</var>. For a more structured approach to programming, use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">while</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span> statements.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"agv1665703005070__note_b32_2ks_hvb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Neither the goto statement nor Label are allowed inside a\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">try</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">catch</span>, or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">finally</span>\n            block.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agv1665703005070__section_om3_3xg_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d121874e185\">Example: goto ProcScript Label</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example deletes the first 1001 records, then exits the\n            current component. This is typically used when a component is defined for transaction\n            processing.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"agv1665703005070__pre_c32_2ks_hvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec \n$1 = 0\nretrieve\n\nstart: ; the label ends with a colon (:)\nif ($1 = 1001)\n store\n exit\nelse\n remocc\n $1 = $1 + 1\nendif\ngoto start ; but no colon is used in the goto line\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ojm1665702766120.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>break</a><p>Set or clear a break point</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gzi1665702766687.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>done</a><p>Return from the ProcScript module without executing further statements.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7527590\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7527590\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "goto Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Branch unconditionally to the specified label. goto Label Example: goto start Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Label String Label of a statement in the current ProcScript module. Return Values None Use Allowed in all component types. Description The goto statement continues execution within the current ProcScript module, beginning at the statement identified by Label . For a more structured approach to programming, use the while or repeat statements. Note: Neither the goto statement nor Label are allowed inside a try , catch , or finally block. Example: goto ProcScript Label The following example deletes the first 1001 records, then exits the current component. This is typically used when a component is defined for transaction processing. operation exec $1 = 0 retrieve start: ; the label ends with a colon (:) if ($1 = 1001) store exit else remocc $1 = $1 + 1 endif goto start ; but no colon is used in the goto line end; exec Copy Related Links break Set or clear a break point done Return from the ProcScript module without executing further statements. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}